data.description: Beautiful, gated community of only 48 homes in Ponderosa Park. Kitchen features upgraded granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, bar for casual dining and opens to a Great Room with living/dining combo to create a spacious Open Concept design. Master retreat is conveniently located on 1st floor, leading out to a spacious backyard. 2nd floor has 2 bedrooms with a small Gameroom area. This is truly a must see!
